results.longDescription: STEVEN SPIELBERG and GEORGE LUCAS bring you the greatest adventurer of all time in a nonstop thrill ride (Richard Corliss, TIME) thats packed with sensational, awe-inspiring spectacles (Roger Ebert, CHICAGO SUN-TIMES). Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crystal Skull finds Indy (Harrison Ford) trying to outrace a brilliant and beautiful agent (Cate Blanchett) for the mystical, all-powerful crystal skull of Akator. Teaming up with a rebellious young biker (Shia LaBeouf) and his spirited original love Marion (Karen Allen), Indy takes you on an action-packed adventure in the exciting tradition of the classic Indiana Jones movies!
